e-1,Creating thread AdService--stress-17497189710,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-07,adservice,adservice-1,calling activated() for helper class org.chaos_mesh.byteman.helper.StressHelper,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-07,adservice,adservice-1,HelperManager.install for helper class org.chaos_mesh.byteman.helper.StressHelper,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-07,adservice,adservice-1,org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer : inserted trigger for AdService--stress-1749718971 in class org.chaos_mesh.chaos_agent.TriggerThread,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-07,adservice,adservice-1,Starting thread AdService--stress-17497189715,出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["adservice-1"], "service_name": ["adservice"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-07"]}, "matched_anomaly": "The system experienced an anomaly from 2025-06-12T09:02:50Z to 2025-06-12T09:15:50Z. Please infer the possible cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-12 09:02:50+00:00 to 2025-06-12 09:15:50+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "从日志分析可以看出，目前主要涉及的是 `adservice` 在节点 `aiops-k8s-07` 上的压力相关异常。这些错误日志表明 `adservice` 进行了大量线程创建和运行，可能导致了该服务的资源消耗增加。然而并未发现与 `aiops-k8s-08` 相关的直接错误日志。\n\n### 错误关键词提取\n- 主要关键词: `stress`, `thread`, `AdService--stress-1749718971`, `org.chaos_mesh.chaos_agent.TriggerThread`\n\n### 组件与原因分析\n- **分析组件**: `adservice` \n- **异常原因**: `adservice` 的压力测试（StressTest）导致线程管理异常和服务资源消耗增加。\n\n### 核心日志片段\n以下日志片段表明 `adservice` 正在进行压力测试：\n- \"Calling installed(AdService--stress-1749718971) for helper class org.jboss.byteman.rule.helper.Helper\"\n- \"Installed rule using default helper : AdService--stress-1749718971\"\n- \"Running thread AdService--stress-17497189714\"\n\n### JSON 输出\n根据当前数据，初始假设 \"aiops-k8s-08 是根因由于 node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes 耗尽影响了 cartservice 和其他服务\" 的提案可能不无问题，更可能的根因是 `adservice` 在进行压力测试导致的资源消耗问题。因此在 stance 字段中标记为 'OPPOSE'。\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"OPPOSE\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"stress\",\n    \"thread\",\n    \"AdService--stress-1749718971\",\n    \"org.chaos_mesh.chaos_agent.TriggerThread\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Adservice 的压力测试导致线程管理异常和服务资源消耗增加\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Calling installed(AdService--stress-1749718971) for helper class org.jboss.byteman.rule.helper.Helper, Installed rule using default helper : AdService--stress-1749718971\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "Based on the metric data obtained from the anomaly analysis tool, we can proceed to evaluate the initial hypothesis regarding the root cause of the anomaly:\n\n### Detected Metric Keys\nAfter parsing the anomaly metrics CSV, the most significant change ratios were detected in the following metrics:\n- `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes` on `aiops-k8s-08`\n- `rrt_max` for `cartservice`\n- `node_cpu_usage_rate` on `aiops-k8s-07`\n\n### Hypothesis Evaluation\n\n#### Hypothesis Details:\n- **Hypothesis Suggestion**: \"aiops-k8s-08 is the root cause due to node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes exhaustion impacting services like cartservice.\"\n  \n#### Supporting Evidence:\n- **Metric Changes**:\n  - `aiops-k8s-08` demonstrated a significant decrease (13.32%) in `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes`, which could lead to memory exhaustion.\n  - `cartservice`, running on `aiops-k8s-08`, exhibited heightened `rrt_max` values during the fault period, indicating increased latency.\n  - The high change ratio in `rrt_max` for `cartservice` aligns with the hypothesis of degraded service performance due to node resource constraints.\n\n#### Opposition Factors:\n- While `node_cpu_usage_rate` on `aiops-k8s-07` increased, it does not correspond directly to the observed cartservice anomalies.\n\n### Conclusion\n\nThe hypothesis centers on the `aiops-k8s-08` memory exhaustion as a root cause affecting `cartservice`. The detected metrics, especially the `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes` and its impact on `rrt_max` of `cartservice` running on the same node, support the hypothesis.\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\n    \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\",\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"node_cpu_usage_rate\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes exhaustion causing performance degradation in services like cartservice\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Significant reduction in node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes by 13.32% and impacts on cartservice rrt_max during the fault period.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nThe hypothesis is supported due to direct evidence linking `aiops-k8s-08` node memory exhaustion to increased latency in `cartservice`.", "trace_analysis_findings": "以下是对链路追踪数据的分析，以及初始假设的验证。\n\n### 分析结果\n\n#### 关键异常链路和指标\n1. `aiops-k8s-08` 节点出现：\n   - **延迟显著增加**: `cartservice->redis` 操作延迟从正常 1739.74ms 上升到 17804.67ms，倍数达到约 10.24。\n   - `cartservice->checkoutservice` 的调用也在此节点监测到明显增长，从正常 1952.23ms 增加到 31668ms，倍数约 16.21。\n\n2. 其他节点主要是：\n   - 各服务调用延迟提升，但幅度较低（如 `shippingservice`, `emailservice`）。\n\n#### 错误类型\n- **延迟指标**:\n  - 关键组件 `cartservice` 在 `aiops-k8s-08` 节点的所有调用链均显著增加。\n- **无连接拒绝错误**: 出现的问题以延迟为主而非直接服务不可用，这表明问题可能源于资源耗尽（CPU/内存）。\n\n#### 调用链趋势和瓶颈定位\n- `cartservice` 操作明显成为瓶颈。\n- 延迟的起始点和最高热点存在于 `aiops-k8s-08`，对应 CPU 使用率和内存消耗同步提升。\n\n### 初始假设验证\n\n基于数据，原始假设 \"`aiops-k8s-08 is the root cause due to node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes exhaustion impacting services like cartservice`\" 可以被支持。具体原因为：\n1. 调用链数据显示 `aiops-k8s-08` 节点的资源耗尽导致延迟激增。\n2. 延迟瓶颈点扩散至下游服务，尤其是 Redis 操作和 Checkout 跨服务通信，间接影响了整个调用拓扑。\n\n### 输出 JSON\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"cartservice->checkoutservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"Node fault (Memory exhaustion caused bottlenecks at cartservice and redis)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Delay spike from cartservice->redis (1739.74ms -> 17804.67ms) and cartservice->checkoutservice (1952.23ms -> 31668ms)\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "current_hypothesis": "aiops-k8s-08 is the root cause due to node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes exhaustion impacting services like cartservice"}
